comments/ooqc4p/borrowing_xmr_at_coinrabbit/h6z923w/?utm_source=reddit&amp;utm_medium=web2x&amp;context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"><div class="styles_answer__7_D9K"><img src="data:image/png;base64," class="styles_avatar__oqfGv" alt="Crypto loans review 1" loading="lazy" width="60" height="60"/><div class="styles_author__yWrEs"><div class="styles_name__bcUdT">Vik Sharma</div><div class="styles_position__Xfo7N">Cake Wallet CEO</div></div></div><header class="styles_header__7iQFS">Reliable, safe and fast Crypto loans</header><div class="styles_body__DgvXi">I&#x27;ve used CoinRabbit multiple times and found their service to be reliable, safe, and fast. The customer service has been spectacular as well. I would recommend this to anyone who wants a loan against their crypto.</div></a></div><div class="styles_slide__LK2Z3"><a href="https://www.g2.com/products/coinrabbit/reviews" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"><div class="styles_answer__7_D9K"><img src="data:image/png;base64," class="styles_avatar__oqfGv" alt="Crypto loans review 2" loading="lazy" width="60" height="60"/><div class="styles_author__yWrEs"><div class="styles_name__bcUdT">Andrew S.</div></div></div><header class="styles_header__7iQFS">Most Reliable Crypto Collateral Loan System There is</header><div class="styles_body__DgvXi">Very reasonable APR rates and no credit checks makes for an easy user experience.</div></a></div><div class="styles_slide__LK2Z3"><a href="https://twitter.com/walerikus/status/1420427814000644099?s=21" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"><div class="styles_answer__7_D9K"><img src="/_next/static/images/valerios-baglaridis-aefab1b7dec692c29a3493794d0d8b6f.png" class="styles_avatar__oqfGv" alt="Crypto loans review 3" loading="lazy" width="60" height="60"/><div class="styles_author__yWrEs"><div class="styles_name__bcUdT">Valerios Baglaridis</div><div class="styles_position__Xfo7N">DGB Influencer</div></div></div><header class="styles_header__7iQFS">By far the best user experience provided by CoinRabbit</header><div class="styles_body__DgvXi">CoinRabbit provides by far the best user experience, and I have tried nexo finances, celsius and various ethereum based defi protocols like MakerDAO and compound finance.</div></a></div><div class="styles_slide__LK2Z3"><a href="https://www.g2.com/products/coinrabbit/reviews" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"><div class="styles_answer__7_D9K"><img src="/_next/static/images/sahad-1ef6857521fd076937aa354ab3de0969.png" class="styles_avatar__oqfGv" alt="Crypto loans review 4" loading="lazy" width="60" height="60"/><div class="styles_author__yWrEs"><div class="styles_name__bcUdT">Sahad N.</div></div></div><header class="styles_header__7iQFS">Hassle free crypto loan in few steps</header><div class="styles_body__DgvXi">Simple, prompt delivery of loans without any trouble. The interface is very easy to use and gets things done. I<!-- -->&#x27;<!-- -->am a regular visitor to the website whenever I am in need. Purely trustable source of money.</div></a></div><div class="styles_slide__LK2Z3"><a href="https://twitter.com/firoorg/status/1403350419279998981?s=21" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"><div class="styles_answer__7_D9K"><img src="data:image/png;base64," class="styles_avatar__oqfGv" alt="Crypto loans review 5" loading="lazy" width="60" height="60"/><div class="styles_author__yWrEs"><div class="styles_name__bcUdT">Reuben</div><div class="styles_position__Xfo7N">FIRO cofounder</div></div></div><header class="styles_header__7iQFS">Seamless and quick FIRO loans without registration</header><div class="styles_body__DgvXi">Getting a stablecoin loan on CoinRabbit using FIRO is seamless and quick without requiring user registration. Its flexibility in having loans with no fixed duration are also very attractive allowing you to hodl your crypto while having USD to spend.</div></a></div><div class="styles_slide__LK2Z3"><a href="https://twitter.com/gokuafrica/status/1421938014897410048?s=21" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"><div class="styles_answer__7_D9K"><img src="data:image/png;base64," class="styles_avatar__oqfGv" alt="Crypto loans review 6" loading="lazy" width="60" height="60"/><div class="styles_author__yWrEs"><div class="styles_name__bcUdT">@Gokuafrika</div></div></div><header class="styles_header__7iQFS">Friendly loan terms: choose when to make payments yourself</header><div class="styles_body__DgvXi">I am still riding the wave. Too early to make any profits off my loans. The cool thing is that by putting crypto as collateral and using your friendly loan terms, I can choose when to make payments to close/partially close loans. This is awesome as this frees me a lot!</div></a></div></div><div class="styles_dotsWrapper__gby_t"><div class="styles_dotsWrapperInner__k66IB"><div class="styles_dot__QfSiZ styles_dotActive__XlKX9" style="left:0px"></div><div class="styles_dot__QfSiZ styles_dotEmpty__9RMqM"></div><div class="styles_dot__QfSiZ styles_dotEmpty__9RMqM"></div><div class="styles_dot__QfSiZ styles_dotEmpty__9RMqM"></div><div class="styles_dot__QfSiZ styles_dotEmpty__9RMqM"></div><div class="styles_dot__QfSiZ styles_dotEmpty__9RMqM"></div><div class="styles_dot__QfSiZ styles_dotEmpty__9RMqM"></div><div class="styles_dotsCage__q0z_Q"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," height="20" width="40" alt="dot-cage-0" loading="lazy"/><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," height="20" width="40" alt="dot-cage-1" loading="lazy"/><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," height="20" width="40" alt="dot-cage-2" loading="lazy"/><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," height="20" width="40" alt="dot-cage-3" loading="lazy"/><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," height="20" width="40" alt="dot-cage-4" loading="lazy"/><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," height="20" width="40" alt="dot-cage-5" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div><div class="styles_swiperButton__vCTXq styles_swiperButtonNext__wiVXf"><div></div></div></div></section><section class="styles_block__dnnjd"><div class="container styles_blockWrapper__MaqOz"><div class="styles_imageBox__pVlec"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:relative;max-width:100%"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;max-width:100%"><img style="display:block;max-width:100%;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0" alt="" aria-hidden="true" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20version=%271.1%27%20width=%27559%27%20height=%27695%27/%3e"/></span><img alt="best bitcoin lending site" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="intrinsic" class="styles_image__2lwRM" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%"/><noscript><img alt="best bitcoin lending site" srcSet="/_next/image/?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fphone-43aacfda8407881a83c07c34cad2bded.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image/?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fphone-43aacfda8407881a83c07c34cad2bded.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image/?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fphone-43aacfda8407881a83c07c34cad2bded.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75" decoding="async" data-nimg="intrinsic" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%" class="styles_image__2lwRM" loading="lazy"/></noscript></span></div><div class="styles_content__dihw4"><h2 class="styles_title__Qr4ui">We&#x27;re always on the watch</h2><div class="styles_contentBox__WSulP"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:relative;max-width:100%"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;max-width:100%"><img style="display:block;max-width:100%;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0" alt="" aria-hidden="true" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20version=%271.1%27%20width=%2752%27%20height=%2752%27/%3e"/></span><img alt="Borrow Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," decoding="async" data-nimg="intrinsic" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%"/></span><p class="styles_contentText__R_T8I">We don&#x27;t want you to lose your crypto, so we monitor your loan every moment of every day.</p><p class="styles_contentText__R_T8I">If your loan reaches any of<!-- --> <b>three limit zones</b>, <!-- -->we will immediately notify you about it by email and sms.</p></div><div class="styles_contentBox__WSulP"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:relative;max-width:100%"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;max-width:100%"><img style="display:block;max-width:100%;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0" alt="" aria-hidden="true" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20version=%271.1%27%20width=%2767%27%20height=%2767%27/%3e"/></span><img alt="cryptocurrency loans worldwide" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," decoding="async" data-nimg="intrinsic" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%"/></span><p class="styles_contentText__R_T8I">Before or after you get your loan, our support team is always ready to help you and answer any of your questions.</p><p class="styles_contentText__R_T8I"><b>24/7 live support</b> <!-- -->is here up for you.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="styles_block__WcV4D" id="how-it-works"><div class="container styles_blockWrapper__6oEUT"><div class="styles_content__izS74"><h2 class="styles_title__Jja4U">FAQ</h2><div class="styles_questionsList__4DZDF"><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>How do crypto loans work?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>With a CoinRabbit crypto loan, you can borrow money using crypto as collateral without selling your holdings. Simply deposit your crypto (BTC, ETH, XRP, or over 300 other supported assets) and receive a loan in stablecoins. Once you repay the loan with interest, your collateral is returned in full. This offers a fast and flexible way to access liquidity while continuing to hold your crypto.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>How does crypto lending work?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>Crypto lending on CoinRabbit works transparently. As the lender, CoinRabbit provides USDT or other supported assets, fully secured by the collateral, so no credit checks are required. This lets borrowers quickly get funds while staying within a secure crypto ecosystem.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>How do you pay back a crypto loan?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>CoinRabbit offers two types of crypto loans. Fixed-term loans require full repayment plus interest by the end of the agreed period though you can repay early. Open-ended loans let you repay anytime, in full or in part, with no set schedule or hidden fees. After full repayment, your collateral is returned immediately.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>Why choose a Bitcoin loan over selling your Bitcoin?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>A Bitcoin loan lets you unlock the value of your Bitcoin without selling it, so you keep full ownership of your Bitcoin and benefit if its price rises. Since Bitcoin is known for its long-term growth potential and volatility, borrowing against it can be a strategic way to access funds without missing out on future gains.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>Can I borrow against my XRP?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>You can take out a loan using XRP as collateral on CoinRabbit, along with a diverse portfolio of over 300 cryptocurrencies. We are actively working to add even more assets to give you greater flexibility and more lending options.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>What interest rate options do you offer?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>At CoinRabbit, interest rates vary depending on several factors including the specific cryptocurrency, loan to value ratio (LTV), and loan term. We offer monthly rates starting from 1.333% and annual percentage rates (APR) beginning at 17%. The rate you agree to when taking out your loan remains fixed for the entire duration of the loan and does not change over time.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>What does an instant crypto loan mean? How fast can I receive the funds?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>An instant crypto loan means you can get funds quickly without lengthy paperwork or credit checks. At CoinRabbit, you typically receive your loan within 10 to 15 minutes after submitting your collateral.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>What happens if my collateral value changes?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>At CoinRabbit, you stay fully informed about your collateral’s value through your personal dashboard, where you can track everything in real time. If the price of your collateral moves into a different risk zone, we will send you immediate notifications so you have time to take action, whether that is adding more collateral or repaying part of your loan. This gives you full control and peace of mind.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>Is there a crypto lending API available for integration?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>CoinRabbit offers a white-labeled crypto lending API for businesses, allowing seamless integration of crypto-backed loans while preserving your branding and user experience. We also provide customized rates and terms for trusted partners, tailored to their preferred assets, volumes, and timelines.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>Does CoinRabbit have a crypto loan app?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>Yes, CoinRabbit offers a comprehensive app that combines a secure crypto wallet, an integrated exchange, and loan management tools, allowing you to efficiently manage your assets in one platform.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>What are fixed-term crypto loans?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>Fixed-term crypto loans at CoinRabbit have a set repayment period (usually 30 days) with interest calculated upfront at a fixed, lower rate. You borrow crypto-backed funds and repay the full amount by the end of the term, with no penalties for early repayment. This provides cost certainty and clear timelines for managing your loan.</p></div></div><div class="styles_tab__dSuqD"><div class="styles_tabHead__SdSoY"><h3>Are crypto loans worth it?</h3><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIGZpbGw9Im5vbmUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PHBhdGggb3BhY2l0eT0iLjUiIGQ9Ik0xMCAyMFYwTTAgMTBoMjAiIHN0cm9rZT0iIzFEMUQxRCIgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPSIuNSIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" alt="IconPlus" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"/></div><div class="styles_tabContent__zKz1l"><p>Crypto loans are helpful for managing short-term expenses, optimizing taxes, or using your crypto to seize trading and investment opportunities. However, whether they’re right for you depends on your personal financial goals and situation.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="styles_image__rTNAI"><img src="/_next/static/images/questions-a4bef390e6d6d0f1d53e716b6660e8e6.png" alt="how to borrow cryptocurrency" width="437" height="404" loading="lazy"/></div></div></section></div></div></div><div id="floating-trustpilot" class="trustpilot-widget" style="display:none;height:0" data-locale="en-US" data-template-id="53aa8807dec7e10d38f59f32" data-businessunit-id="5fa44c2c9262500001e6a79a" data-style-height="58" data-style-width="145" data-theme="dark"><a href="https://www.trustpilot.com/review/coinrabbit.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"></a></div><div class="styles_footer__VTXj9"><div class="container styles_footerContainer__VsOG2"><div class="styles_rightBlock__XDldb"><div><div class="styles_copyright__OtN7v"><a href="/"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="CoinRabbit" width="123" height="25" loading="lazy"/></a><p class="styles_copyrightText__yqn5s">2025<!-- --> © Coinrabbit</p></div></div><div class="styles_column__xL3Cs"><p>Crypto Loans</p><div class="styles_innerColumn__S7r44"><a href="/loans/btc/">Bitcoin (BTC) loan</a><a href="/loans/ltc/">Litecoin (LTC) loan</a><a href="/loans/eth/">Ethereum (ETH) loan</a><a href="/coin/mog/">Mog Coin (MOG) loan</a><a href="/loans/xrp/">XRP (XRP) loan</a><a href="/loans/dash/">Dash (DASH) loan</a><a href="/loans/sol/">Solana (SOL) loan</a><a href="/loans/uni/">Uniswap (UNI) loan</a><a href="/loans/usdt/">Tether (USDT) loan</a><a href="/loans/vet/">VeChain (VET) loan</a><a href="/loans/usdc/">USD Coin (USDC) loan</a><a href="/coin/kaia/">Kaia (KAIA) loan</a><a href="/loans/ada/">Cardano (ADA) loan</a><a href="/loans/doge/">Doge (DOGE) loan</a><a href="/loans/aave/">Aave (AAVE) loan</a><a href="/">Loan Calculator</a><a href="/loans/dot/">Polkadot (DOT) loan</a></div></div><div class="styles_column__xL3Cs"><